title: ‘Suspicious’ Windows update was the result of a test error, says Microsoft
text:
‘Suspicious’ Windows update was the result of a test error, says Microsoft 
Published By: DigitalTrends.com - Today 
Microsoft says a test error was responsible for a suspicious-looking Windows 7 update that was issued today, but the company has not confirm...
